<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.4.1">
<l>veṇṇe yaḷainta kuṇuṅkum viḷaiyāṭu puḻutiyuṅ koṇṭu</l>
<l>tiṇṇeṉa vivvirā vuṉṉait tēyttuk kiṭakkanā ṉoṭṭē</l>
<l>ṉeṇṇey puḷippaḻaṅ koṇṭiṅ kettaṉai pōtu miruntēṉ</l>
<l>naṇṇa lariya pirāṉē nāraṇā nīrāṭa vārāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I certainly do not agree [to let] you go to sleep this night,</l>
<l>rubbing [all over the bed] with the smell of cattle</l>
<l rend="indent">mixed with butter and the dirt [you] played [in].</l>
<l>With the gingili oil and tamarind fruit, I will be here for however long.</l>
<l>O Lord who is difficult to approach, O Narana, come to [take your] bath.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
